name: podamShouldNotcreateInstancesOfNonInstantiableClasses

testSteps.description: Given a Podam Factory with external factory uk.co.jemos.podam.test.unit.features.externalFactory.TestExternalFactory@1a5fdeb

Then the two objects uk.co.jemos.podam.test.unit.features.externalFactory.TestExternalFactory@1a5fdeb and uk.co.jemos.podam.test.unit.features.externalFactory.TestExternalFactory@1a5fdeb should be equal
When I invoke the factory manufacturing for class uk.co.jemos.podam.test.dto.NonInstantiatableClass
Then the object should be null
Then the two objects 1 and 1 should be equal
Then the two objects class uk.co.jemos.podam.test.dto.NonInstantiatableClass and class uk.co.jemos.podam.test.dto.NonInstantiatableClass should be equal
Then the two objects 0 and 0 should be equal

title: Podam should not create instances of non-instantiable classes
